      • getReferencedModePart

        public EntityValuedModelPart getReferencedModePart()
        Description copied from interface: FetchParent
        Whereas FetchParent.getReferencedMappingContainer() and FetchParent.getReferencedMappingType() return the referenced container type, this method returns the referenced part. E.g. for a many-to-one this methods returns the ToOneAttributeMapping while FetchParent.getReferencedMappingContainer() and FetchParent.getReferencedMappingType() return the referenced EntityMappingType.
        Specified by:
